This annex describes usages of this module.
Equipment on a ship requires power through an interface (identified as 'Panel power supply'). The interface specification belongs to the product categories "POWER" and "IFS".
#2000= PRODUCT('Panel power supply',' ','Interface identity for record purposes only',(#2020)); #2010= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('interface',$,(#2000)); #2020= PRODUCT_CONTEXT('marine',#2030,'interface management'); #2030= APPLICATION_CONTEXT('Product life-cycle support'); #2040= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('IFS','Category',(#2000)); #2050= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('POWER','Type',(#2000));
The interface specification has a version (identified as 'SN0001 design').
#2060= PRODUCT_DEFINITION_FORMATION('SN0001 design',$,#2000);
A power supply (identified as '420V 50Hz') and an alarm panel (identified as 'Panel RG 431') require connectors.
#2070= PRODUCT('420V 50Hz','power supply connector',$,(#2020)); #2080= PRODUCT('Panel RG 431','alarm panel connector',$,(#2020)); #2090= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('interface connector',$,(#2070,#2080));
The panel connector has a design.
#2100= INTERFACE_CONNECTOR_DESIGN('Panel RG 431 - connector design',$,#2080);
Actual connectors exist. The actual panel connector corresponds to the panel connector design.
#2110= INTERFACE_CONNECTOR_AS_REALIZED('420V 50Hz - A',$,#2070); #2120= INTERFACE_CONNECTOR_AS_REALIZED('Panel RG 431 - A',$,#2080); #2130= INTERFACE_CONNECTOR_DESIGN_TO_REALIZED('Panel RG 431 - A design',' ',$,#2100,#2120);
The actual connectors are part of an actual power supply and actual alarm panel.
#2140= PRODUCT_DEFINITION('420V 50Hz - A',$,#2110,#2220); #2150= PRODUCT_DEFINITION('Panel RG 431 - A',$,#2120,#2220); #2160= PRODUCT('Panel RG 431','alarm panel',$,(#2020)); #2170= PRODUCT('420V 50Hz','power supply',$,(#2020)); #2180= PRODUCT_AS_REALIZED('Panel RG 431 - A',$,#2160); #2190= PRODUCT_AS_REALIZED('420V 50Hz - A',$,#2170); #2200= PRODUCT_DEFINITION('Panel RG 431 - A',$,#2180,#2220); #2210= PRODUCT_DEFINITION('420V 50Hz - A',$,#2190,#2220); #2220= PRODUCT_DEFINITION_CONTEXT('operational configuration',#2030,'in-service'); #2230= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('part',$,(#2160,#2170)); #2240= CONNECTOR_ON('420V 50Hz - A',' ',$,#2140,#2210); #2250= CONNECTOR_ON('Panel RG 431 - A',' ',$,#2150,#2200);
The actual connectors are connected.
#2260= INTERFACE_CONNECTION('SN0001',' ',$,#2150,#2140);
The connectors conform to the interface specification.
#2290= PRODUCT_DEFINITION('SN0001',$,#2060,#2220); #2300= INTERFACE_DEFINITION_FOR(#2140,#2290); #2310= INTERFACE_DEFINITION_FOR(#2150,#2290);
